DATA ATTRIBUTION:

This software uses publicly available data from the following sources:

1. Tao, L., et al. (2017). "Techno-economic analysis and life-cycle assessment 
   of cellulosic isobutanol and comparison with cellulosic ethanol and n-butanol." 
   Green Chemistry, DOI: 10.1039/C6GC02800D

2. Han, J., et al. (2017). "Life-cycle analysis of bio-based aviation fuels." 
   Biotechnology for Biofuels, DOI: 10.1186/s13068-017-0698-z

3. GREET Model (2023). Argonne National Laboratory. 
   Available at: https://greet.es.anl.gov

Users must cite these original sources when publishing results derived from this code.
